            "answer_feedback": "Your opposition is shocked at your promises, but there's no way, in their eyes, you manage to keep them. Your staffers are dismayed by your dismissive attitude. Whatever happened to the bombastic campaigner you once were? You were the opposite in '62, what's different now?"
