            "candidate": 92,
            "answer_feedback": "The media are vultures. They'll rip you apart for a good story, every red-blooded American knows this. You lose everywhere it matters, but you'll keep those red-blooded boys from real America. They'll be even more loyal to you. You can never trust a journalist."
