        "pk": 12902,
        "fields": {
            "answer": 12899,
            "candidate": 92,
            "answer_feedback": "It's very obvious to anyone paying attention as to what you're doing. But to the disillusioned in the DNC convention hall, and those who protest outside, your words ring true within their minds. You couldn't be more different than those radicals, yet it's almost admirable how they operate. Like brainless unkempt meat shields so confidently running at the law. Almost."
